# 🚀 Day 83/90 – Health Interpretation Card

Congratulations! 🎉

Yesterday you made the Report Details screen look professional.

Today you'll make it **smarter** by showing a simple health interpretation based on the hemoglobin value.

---

# 🎯 Today's Goal

Instead of only showing:

```text
Hemoglobin : 13.5
```

The screen will also show:

```text
🩺 Health Interpretation

Hemoglobin is within the normal range.

Status : Healthy
```

or

```text
🩺 Health Interpretation

Hemoglobin is below the normal range.

Status : Low Hemoglobin
```

